OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening, with warm sunny spells. Dry
OL,7,Fwith variable amounts of cloud
OL,8,Fovernight. Some mist lingering along
OL,9,Fsome coastal districts. Perhaps some
OL,10,Fpatchy low cloud affecting western
OL,11,Fhills by the end of the night. Winds
OL,12,Fremaining light.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FA similar day to Wednesday
OL,15,Fwith plenty of sunshine and turning
OL,16,Fvery warm or hot by the afternoon. A
OL,17,Fcooler, onshore breeze might develop
OL,18,Fnear coasts of Yorkshire later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
